sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KServeGW as KServe Ingress<br/>TLS Termination
    participant API as vLLM API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant MultiModel as MultiModelAsyncLLM
    participant Runner as HPUModelRunner
    participant Worker as HPUWorker
    participant HPU as Gaudi HPU Device
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NIXL as Other vLLM Instance<br/>(NIXL KV Transfer)

    Note over Client,HPU: Flow 1: Model Inference Request

    Client->>KServeGW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (platform)
    KServeGW->>API: Forward (TLS terminated)<br/>HTTP/8000
    API->>Runner: Schedule inference<br/>In-process Python
    Runner->>HPU: Execute forward pass<br/>HPU API (habana-frameworks)<br/>Graph compiled, bucketed
    HPU-->>Runner: Inference result
    Runner-->>API: Prediction tokens
    API-->>KServeGW: SSE streaming response<br/>HTTP/8000
    KServeGW-->>Client: JSON/SSE Response

    Note over Client,HPU: Flow 2: Multi-Model Switch (dev mode)

    Client->>API: POST /v1/models/switch<br/>{"model": "new-model"}<br/>Gate: VLLM_SERVER_DEV_MODE=1
    API->>MultiModel: Switch model request
    MultiModel->>Worker: sleep() - move weights HPU→CPU
    Worker->>HPU: Release HPU memory
    HPU-->>Worker: Memory freed
    MultiModel->>Worker: unload_model()
    MultiModel->>Worker: load_model("new-model")
    Worker->>HFHub: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer HF_TOKEN
    HFHub-->>Worker: Model artifacts
    Worker->>HPU: Load weights to HPU<br/>Compile graphs
    HPU-->>Worker: Model ready
    MultiModel-->>API: Switch complete
    API-->>Client: 200 OK {"status": "switched"}

    Note over NIXL,HPU: Flow 3: Disaggregated KV Transfer (NIXL)

    Note right of Worker: Prefill instance completes<br/>prompt processing
    Worker->>NIXL: KV cache transfer<br/>RDMA/TCP (dynamic port)<br/>No encryption, trust-based
    NIXL-->>Worker: KV cache received
    Note right of Worker: Decode instance continues<br/>token generation from KV cache
